From b213e4f3b2c56445fdf1cbf85b66646760e85dca Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: ufoptg <perthgroups@protonmail.com>
Date: Wed, 1 Jul 2026 10:53:08 +0000
Subject: [PATCH 1/5] feat(spotify): add Spotify integration on top of main
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

Ported from ufoptg/meld (dev branch) as a focused, minimal integration
onto MuSicX's main branch. No merge — surgical file copy + wiring.

Modules added:
  - :spotify        (Kotlin/JVM, Spotify web-player API + TOTP auth)
  - :paxsenix       already present in main; kept main's version

App-level files added (Spotify-only, 30 files):
  - db/entities/SpotifyMatchEntity.kt
  - models/SpotifyHomeSection.kt, NewReleaseItem.kt
  - playback/Spotify{MetadataRegistry,ProfileCache,RecommendationEngine,YouTubeMapper}.kt
  - playback/queues/Spotify{Queue,PlaylistQueue,LikedSongsQueue}.kt
  - utils/Spotify{HashSync,ItemConverter,TokenManager}.kt
  - viewmodels/Spotify{,Album,Playlist,LikedSongs,Preload}ViewModel.kt
  - ui/screens/SpotifyLoginScreen.kt (WebView + sp_dc cookie extraction)
  - ui/screens/album/SpotifyAlbumScreen.kt
  - ui/screens/library/SpotifyFolderScreen.kt
  - ui/screens/playlist/Spotify{Playlist,LikedSongs}Screen.kt
  - ui/screens/settings/integrations/Spotify{Settings,PreloadScreen}.kt
  - ui/menu/Spotify{TrackMenu,PlaylistPickerDialog,PlaylistPinMenu}.kt
  - ui/component/Spotify{FolderListItem,HomeSectionRow}.kt, YouTubeMatchDialog.kt
  - ui/component/PreferenceGroupTitle.kt (extracted from meld)

Modifications to existing files:
  - settings.gradle.kts       add :spotify
  - app/build.gradle.kts       add project(':spotify') dependency
  - AndroidManifest.xml       add Spotify OAuth callback (musicx://spotify/callback)
  - App.kt                    add Spotify.logger, SpotifyHashSync, SpotifyTokenManager init
  - constants/PreferenceKeys.kt   add 18 Spotify preference keys + SpotifySortType enum
                                  + HideYtmLikedSongsKey
  - db/MusicDatabase.kt       add SpotifyMatchEntity entity, version bump 38 → 39
                                  + AutoMigration(from=38, to=39)
  - db/DatabaseDao.kt         add 4 spotify_match DAO methods
  - ui/screens/NavigationBuilder.kt   add 7 Spotify routes
  - ui/screens/settings/integrations/IntegrationScreen.kt   add Spotify entry point
  - res/values/metrolist_strings.xml   add ~80 Spotify UI strings
  - res/drawable/spotify.xml   Spotify logo

Adjustments to imported meld files:
  - SpotifyTrackMenu.kt: stripped Qobuz dependency (Qobuz not ported)
  - SpotifySettings.kt : stripped 137-line Qobuz section + QobuzBackendHealthSection

No Podcasts/Qobuz/SponsorBlock/Recognition-Widget/LyricsPlus features from meld
were carried in — this is a focused Spotify-only integration.

Spotify auth uses web-player token flow (sp_dc cookie + TOTP from community
GitHub Gist). No Spotify Developer Client ID/Secret required.
