+    /**
+     * Adds tracks to a Spotify playlist via GQL mutation.
+     * @param playlistId Playlist ID (without the `spotify:playlist:` prefix).
+     * @param trackUris Full Spotify URIs, e.g. `["spotify:track:abc123"]`.
